### 2.3 Логика входа — [login.php](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive/Desktop/kenes/public/login.php)

```php
$sql = "SELECT id, full_name, email, password_hash, 'customer' as user_type, ...
        FROM customers WHERE email = ?
        UNION ALL
        SELECT id, full_name, email, password_hash, 'consultant' as user_type, ...
        FROM consultants WHERE email = ?";

$stmt = $pdo->prepare($sql);
$stmt->execute([$email, $email]);
$user = $stmt->fetch();

if ($user && password_verify($password, $user['password_hash'])) {
    $_SESSION['user_id'] = $user['id'];
    $_SESSION['user_type'] = $user['user_type'];
    // ... сохранение данных в сессию
    header('Location: ' . ($user['user_type'] === 'consultant'
        ? 'consultant-dashboard.php' : 'customer-dashboard.php'));
}
```

| Аспект | Описание |
|--------|----------|
| **Поиск пользователя** | `UNION ALL` запрос ищет email одновременно в `customers` и `consultants` |
| **Хеширование пароля** | `password_verify()` — проверка bcrypt-хеша |
| **Сессия** | Сохраняет `user_id`, `user_name`, `user_email`, `user_type` |
| **Remember Me** | Продлевает cookie сессии на 30 дней |
| **Защита** | CSRF-верификация через [verifyCsrf()](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive/Desktop/kenes/public/includes/auth_guard.php#40-51) |

