### 2.8 Библиотека алгоритмов — [js/algorithms.js](file:///c:/Users/User/OneDrive/Desktop/kenes/public/js/algorithms.js)

```javascript
// Поиск
function linearSearch(arr, target)  → O(n)
function binarySearch(arr, target)  → O(log n), требует sorted array

// Сортировка
function bubbleSort(arr)     → O(n²), stable, in-place
function insertionSort(arr)  → O(n²), stable, in-place
function quickSort(arr)      → O(n log n) avg, unstable, new array
function mergeSort(arr)      → O(n log n), stable, new array
function merge(left, right)  → Helper для mergeSort
```

| Алгоритм | Время (avg) | Время (worst) | Пространство | Стабильность |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Linear Search | O(n) | O(n) | O(1) | — |
| Binary Search | O(log n) | O(log n) | O(1) | — |
| Bubble Sort | O(n²) | O(n²) | O(1) | ✅ Stable |
| Insertion Sort | O(n²) | O(n²) | O(1) | ✅ Stable |
| Quick Sort | O(n log n) | O(n²) | O(n) | ❌ Unstable |
| Merge Sort | O(n log n) | O(n log n) | O(n) | ✅ Stable |

